Brief History of the Company

       We are engaged in the manufacture and supply of RCC Spun Pipes and collars in different Class and Sizes (NP2, NP3, NP4, P1, P2, P3). Cisterns, Pump Houses, R.C.C. Dustbins and other concrete products.

       We are in the manufacturing activity for the Past 40 years, the pipes are manufactured in various places in Karnataka, i. e, Tumkur & Bengaluru.

        The pipes are catering to mainly NHAI and other projects like BMIC, Bengaluru International Airport & State Highways and other Government agencies like PWD, Zillaparishad, Gramapanchayat, Lift Irrigation Schemes, Outer ring roads, Peripheral Road, RDPR, BWSSB Departments, BBMP etc.,

        We are well equipped with good infrastructure for casting of Pipes and testing equipment for analysis of raw materials and finished products. The pipes are manufactured and tested as per IS 458/2003 standards.

Mr. N. Ashwathnarayan, B.E. (Mech) Managing Director of the company is having experience of above 40 years in this field as well as in other manufacturing activities. This company has professionally managed team to control day to day production, quality control, sales etc
